{"tid":233793,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"(iOS JB) KuaiDial 香港電話黑名單","createTime":"2017-05-07T18:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T17:05:55.000Z","uid":40310,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ef1027a1cc5ca4b5067f40dd180c03ba219489f","tid":233793,"uid":40310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T18:30:09.000Z","msg":"有用開 KuaiDial (來電 block call app) 嘅巴絲，你地應該都有聽聞過以前 &quot;檸七&quot; 及 &quot;鬼知&quot; 巴打定期製作嘅 KuaiDial 電話黑名單，以前可在 Cydia 下載，不過好耐已經冇更新<br />\n<br />\n我喺度正式宣佈我已經接手左呢個咁艱巨嘅任務 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以後大概每一個禮拜我會更新個黑名單一次，有需要嘅可以喺 Cydia 加呢個 repo<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://seemebreakthis.github.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fseemebreakthis.github.io&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b9e67b25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">seemebreakthis.github.io</a><br />\n<br />\n加左之後，repo 入邊得一個 package 可供 download, 又或者你可以 search &quot;Kuaidial Hong Kong Blacklist&quot;, 我個黑名單就會顯示出來 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adb54fa9cabc5ec8b9925f55c48c2eb4b6a6890","tid":233793,"uid":19929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T20:08:32.000Z","msg":"支持巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cd55a26e0cf96d6413116e6dbf7354fb8f1a86","tid":233793,"uid":26700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T23:59:57.000Z","msg":"Thx"},{"pid":"1d51fb5ae8a44cc2fd99000d5fdc08292de29310","tid":233793,"uid":6791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T00:07:10.000Z","msg":"Support"},{"pid":"7aefe73c59468c03ef3f89848c4b50000e46ac23","tid":233793,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T00:59:43.000Z","msg":"無JB但support 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /